qahramon

Enum AnchorType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<AnchorType>
      • qahramon.AnchorType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<AnchorType>

    @Value
public enum AnchorType
extends java.lang.Enum<AnchorType>
    An enumeration of anchor types. In its current definition, the class only distinguishes between right hand, left hand, belt, back and body anchors. With each anchor , a name and id is associated.
    Version:
    1.0 - 2019
    Author:
    Robin Bruneel, Jean-Louis Carron, Edward Wiels
